{"tid":2017153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察協會言論屢違政治中立","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:26:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"731147b131861164dbbc4cd010dd26b7ab74d8fc","tid":2017153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/TD6EFYE3AN7PTS5L7GJLEV7WYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FTD6EFYE3AN7PTS5L7GJLEV7WYQ%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4317acbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FTD6EFYE3AN7PTS5L7GJLEV7WYQ%2F&h=738da6d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/TD6EFYE3AN7PTS5L7GJLEV7WYQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n警察協會言論屢違政治中立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589474122_0d38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589474122_0d38.jpg&h=9a1c8f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林志偉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網上有群組積極發動退休警登記成為立法會換屆選舉票站工作人員，更明言是。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。擔心退休警會否將「仇黃」帶入票站，針對民主派選民及候選人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：建制區選大敗賴票站職員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林志偉曾抹黑民主派<br />\n<br />\n自去年抗爭運動爆發，多個警察協會多次高調指斥民主派，當中警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉言論最受爭議，他及相關警。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n豪及區諾軒在旺角街頭監察警方濫暴問題，林翌日去信立會主席梁君彥，要求正視個別議員專業操守。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。徒及相關議員行為，惟最終去年底區選卻是民主派大勝。<br />\n<br />\n其他三個警察協會，即警司協會、香港警務督察協會及海外督察協會，亦跟員佐級協會沆瀣。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n開批評，指摘段公開信「內容偏頗」，更質疑他在培育學生及管理教育機構的能力，遜於其學術成就。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳珏明"},{"pid":"ae21e2d05281057d19d7f829f6a372ca67ff622e","tid":2017153,"uid":224657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:37:18.000Z","msg":"狗：咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8c374a598a99fb54c716e471ad5b1111e6ba81","tid":2017153,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}